flowRoot.flowPara: An FPGA Implementation of a Nintendo Entertainment System
The current tile index is read from the RAM. This index is then used to grab the tile data from ROM.
These Values are then passed into shift registers. Where they are selected by the fine adjustment of the horizontal scrolling.
